DOWNLOAD JAVA HERE : 

https://www.java.com/en/download/manual.jsp

Copy Java path after shown bin file

now open edit the system environment variables in windows and paste the path

Now download cloudsim file and common math and extract both file 

now open common math and copy first jar file and paste in on cloudsim jar folder 

now copy clousim folder and paste it in document folder

Now download ECLIPSE IDE FOR JAVA DEVELOPERS

open ECLIPSE and Create Java Proj

add location where you paste the cloudsim in Documents

after click next and finish 

now left side click arrow and select examples and double click 1 example and run 



